{"id":232936279,"title":"歷年股王的興衰，誰與爭鋒呢?","content":"世界上股價最高的是巴菲特所創辦的公司叫做波克夏，而台股在歷史的洪流中，也創造了許多股王，這些股王你還記得嗎?  當年風行一時的股王，到現在變成怎樣了呢? \n當年每一檔的股王，都是人人追捧的對象，甚至說出一套非買不可的理由，現在看來雖然都非常的荒唐，但當時的人們卻是深信不疑，使得很多投資人套在當年的最高點，現在回想還會非常的心痛，但歷史卻是不斷的重演，股王也一直興起，到現在股王依舊是人人追捧的對象，讓我們來回顧一下歷史有哪些股王，這些股王又是怎樣的被吹捧的吧!\nhttps://freekongkong.com/the-rise-and-decline-of-stock-kings-over-the-years-who-is-fighting/\nhttps://i.imgur.com/e8vccXW.png","excerpt":"世界上股價最高的是巴菲特所創辦的公司叫做波克夏，而台股在歷史的洪流中，也創造了許多股王，這些股王你還記得嗎？  當年風行一時的股王，到現在變成怎樣了呢？當年每一檔的股王，都是人人追捧的對象，甚至說出一","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"3bceb81c-574e-4a96-8050-4df56096d0df","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-22T04:10:05.239Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T04:10:05.239Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":14,"tags":[],"topics":["投資","理財","股票","台股","證券"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"理財","forumAlias":"money","school":"天空有點灰","department":"girl02675","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":13},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/e8vccXW.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"8fcc2688-be85-4ede-8641-dc6a3b939fb7","url":"https://i.imgur.com/e8vccXWl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/e8vccXWl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/e8vccXWl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-22T04:10:05.239Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T04:10:05.239Z"},{"id":"8fcc2688-be85-4ede-8641-dc6a3b939fb7","url":"https://i.imgur.com/e8vccXW.png","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/e8vccXW","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/e8vccXWl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-22T04:10:05.239Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T04:10:05.2